WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.940 --> 00:00:06.100
 6吋 Material: a. Cream cheese 100g salt-free cream 20g fine sugar 15g milk 85g egg yolk 2 corn flour 10g low-gluten flour 25g b. protein 2 lemon juice 1/2 teaspoon fine sugar 40g 

00:00:09.320 --> 00:00:19.660
 First layer of aluminum foil in the baking mold 

00:00:20.060 --> 00:00:39.100
 Put a layer of cream (outside the size) and put a white newspaper 

00:00:39.940 --> 00:00:48.880
 Corn flour and low-gluten flour are sieved 

00:00:49.160 --> 00:01:04.620
 Protein and egg yolk apart 

00:01:05.460 --> 00:01:11.920
 Protein uses a whisk to make a little foam first. 

00:01:12.380 --> 00:01:28.320
 Then add lemon juice and 1/2 serving of fine sugar for high speed whipping 

00:01:32.480 --> 00:01:36.300
 The bubble has changed and the remaining sugar is added. 

00:01:36.420 --> 00:01:51.220
 High-speed whipping to the end of the bent state (wet foaming) 

00:01:55.920 --> 00:02:06.140
 Cream cheese is stirred into a creamy 

00:02:08.760 --> 00:02:21.140
 Add unsalted cream and mix evenly 

00:02:21.660 --> 00:02:29.300
 Add fine sugar and mix evenly 

00:02:30.180 --> 00:02:48.840
 Add milk and mix evenly 

00:02:51.420 --> 00:03:09.300
 Heat until the cream cheese and fine sugar are completely melted and leave the fire (no need to boil) 

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:15.600
 Add the egg yolk to mix evenly after cooling to 50 degrees c 

00:03:16.940 --> 00:03:33.140
 Add powder to mix evenly 

00:03:34.540 --> 00:04:05.700
 1/3 serving of meringue is added evenly 

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:48.600
 Pour into the remaining meringue and mix evenly 

00:04:50.300 --> 00:04:55.200
 Pour into the baking mold 

00:04:56.620 --> 00:04:59.200
 Tap a few times 

00:04:59.980 --> 00:05:02.280
 Put in a deep baking dish 

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:07.540
 Pour 300g of boiling water into the baking tray 

00:05:08.980 --> 00:05:23.360
 Bake in an oven that has been preheated to 180 ° C for 15 minutes until the surface is colored. Adjust the oven temperature to 120 ° C and continue to bake for 35-40 minutes. 

00:05:28.680 --> 00:05:31.820
 Remove the baking tray 

00:05:33.100 --> 00:05:43.140
 Slightly enclose the edge 

00:05:45.580 --> 00:05:51.920
 Carrying the cake out of the baking mold with the edge of the aluminum foil 

00:05:55.340 --> 00:06:13.100
 Tear off the paper to cool 

00:06:15.240 --> 00:06:20.680
 a mirrored pectin on the surface 

00:06:21.680 --> 00:06:26.620
 Sealed and placed in the refrigerator for 5-6 hours 

00:06:35.140 --> 00:06:47.600
 Tear off the bottom baking paper 

00:06:49.960 --> 00:06:58.380
 The knife is slightly warmed and then cut beautifully. 

00:07:20.140 --> 00:07:23.040
 Enjoy! 

